<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.2">
<l>uyyum vakaiyuṇṭu coṉaceyyi lulakēḻu moḻiyāmai muṉanāḷ</l>
<l>meyyi ṉaḷavēya mutuceyya valavaiya ṉavaṉmēvu nakartāṉ</l>
<l>maiya varivaṇṭu matuvuṇṭu kiḷaiyōṭu malarkiṇṭi yataṉmēl</l>
<l>naiva ḷanaviṟṟu poḻilnantipuraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The means of being saved exists, if [you] do what [I] say!</l>
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram with groves where a black-striped bee,</l>
<l>Sipping nectar with its kin, burrowing into blossoms,</l>
<l rend="indent">thereafter hums a hill tune,</l>
<l>The city where dwells the master who was able to eat, long ago,</l>
<l rend="indent">the seven world to the [full] extent of his body,</l>
<l rend="indent">without leaving [anything].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
